    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Incremental game where you click buttons, pull levers and learn to deal with obsession.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the Machine, understand what makes it tick, become a gear in its perfect system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023620/extras/845e61845b5e225f5ddc6c9625aa309e.poster.avif?t=1770406338\" width=720 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023620/extras/845e61845b5e225f5ddc6c9625aa309e.webm?t=1770406338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023620/extras/845e61845b5e225f5ddc6c9625aa309e.mp4?t=1770406338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Operate the modules of the Machine in an intuitive and tactile way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Repair broken Mechanisms, upgrade, unlock and buy new ones. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pull levers and rotate valves using physics, type in commands in a realistic terminal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023620/extras/e23ad87736c7769c2ae30a9814ed8fac.poster.avif?t=1770406338\" width=720 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023620/extras/e23ad87736c7769c2ae30a9814ed8fac.webm?t=1770406338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023620/extras/e23ad87736c7769c2ae30a9814ed8fac.mp4?t=1770406338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's more to the Machine that meets the eye.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover its secrets, search for the hidden truth that lies beyond the cold exterior.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Use Scanner to see the unseen. Solve escape room style puzzles and learn the inner workings of your Mechanisms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023620/extras/91faa07c65dddf3bdbcc181ce1927593.poster.avif?t=1770406338\" width=720 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023620/extras/91faa07c65dddf3bdbcc181ce1927593.webm?t=1770406338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023620/extras/91faa07c65dddf3bdbcc181ce1927593.mp4?t=1770406338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a break from your Sisyphean task.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tune out the ever present noise of the machinery and fill the silence with some chill music. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go ourside, unwind, relax. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >But remember:  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023620/extras/27a46753ea3aaa98d9a0c98ecd154a3b.poster.avif?t=1770406338\" width=720 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023620/extras/27a46753ea3aaa98d9a0c98ecd154a3b.webm?t=1770406338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023620/extras/27a46753ea3aaa98d9a0c98ecd154a3b.mp4?t=1770406338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
